{"tid":1249410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際騙局：日本人已經講緊恭喜撤回，有twitter嘅唔該RT爆佢","createTime":"2019-06-21T17:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T06:20:30.000Z","uid":234730,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2dc80236afeb19bac8f604b6cdf59568705a080c","tid":1249410,"uid":234730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:08:18.000Z","msg":"第一次開po<br />\n<br />\n日本新聞報導香港政府已將修例廢除<br />\n<br />\n日本新聞報導：香港政府完全停止條例工作，接受明年7月改正案變成廢案。【圖】<br />\n誤導日本民眾以為條例已經撤回，恭喜香港抗爭成功。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SQGAug7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSQGAug7.png&h=5302dcf1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QHdfug8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQHdfug8.png&h=98d6359e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink：<br />\n<a href=\"https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20190621-00000217-kyodonews-int\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadlines.yahoo.co.jp%2Fhl%3Fa%3D20190621-00000217-kyodonews-int&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0PkYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=8523801f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20190621-00000217-kyodonews-int</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.livedoor.com/lite/article_detail/16657928/?_from=linenews_social\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.livedoor.com%2Flite%2Farticle_detail%2F16657928%2F%3F_from%3Dlinenews_social&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0PkYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=5f841789\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.livedoor.com/lite/article_detail/16657928/?_from=linenews_social</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但實際上我哋嘅4大要求係一樣都未達成，<br />\n<br />\n呢度開咗個for日本人睇嘅twitter ac<br />\n各位巴絲如果有用開twitter or有認識日本朋友，麻煩大家幫手share出去啊！！<br />\n<br />\n&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKPEOPLE1/status/1142113931432906752\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKPEOPLE1%2Fstatus%2F1142